{"tid":923872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★東涌之週常！「瞓喺地下，餐廳逼爆，超市排長龍，買晒啲日用品」","createTime":"2018-12-01T15:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T12:11:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d907d359251ec7020d5b3b592582ca6cae1a60e0","tid":923872,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"東網記者今日(1日)巡視東涌，發現仍有大批旅客坐滿廣場空間，商場人山人海，有東涌居民表示，旅客量與以往數周相若。<br />\n<br />\n居民黃先生表示，本周末廣場仍坐滿旅客，「（旅客）瞓喺地下都有，餐廳仍然逼爆，超市排長龍，旅客買晒啲日用品」，他對此感到無奈。黃認為在香港旅檢大樓內加開商店無助改善旅客逼爆東涌情況，因經大橋來港的旅客非特意來購物，他們主要遊覽香港，「見到好多旅客嚟到東涌根本無行街坐喺廣場」，他認為只能等待遊客對大橋的新鮮感減弱，東涌的旅客量才會減少。<br />\n<br />\n居民麥小姐稱，周末經過東薈城仍見大批旅客，「旅客坐晒地下，行去港鐵都非常騷擾」，又認為垃圾量增加，東涌衞生環境變差，她不滿港府針對大橋的配套不足，應增購物點及改善交通配套。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181201/photo/bkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181201222435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181201222435&h=95ef3426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181201/photo/bkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181201222435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181201222435&h=cdf19d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181201/bkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181201%2Fbkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001.html&d=Jg%2B7rGYuEHm6f31NpujP30%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9d8cfdaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181201/bkn-20181201184953532-1201_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7ad506f22adaebaef348d1c8e570bdb4082101d","tid":923872,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0498bdf5a2751e3e52fed84dfdea3d063d6615","tid":923872,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"搵區議員周浩鼎同鄧家彪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e945bc5b43b0f4d00d446727b4ec66eb6651cda8","tid":923872,"uid":81518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b2743544e240758c6b3ebaa57af650c469bd1c","tid":923872,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccaed50c4764709eb56ef68061f4793c115f71df","tid":923872,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"早幾年嘅屯門上水沙田等地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}